Name: Alien X
About the game: Alien X - is a hardcore game where you will have to survive playing like a monster Bomber who is on an unknown planet. It’s a typical platformer where you will do various hardcore levels collecting different items on your way. The main aim during the whole game is to help Bomber to leave the planet. Don’t think it will be easy. You’ll meet traps and flying monsters, so think carefully every your step, watch enemies, collect the things. It will be really thrilling! After you collect everything you can easily do the next level. Go ahead to adventures good luck!
